'''Atle Sveinung Eide''' (born 1957) is a [[Norway|Norwegian]] businessperson, and since 2007 partner with [[HitecVision Private Equity]].<ref name=hitec>{{cite web|url=http://www.hitecvision.com/htv/public/openIndex/view/page1.html?ARTICLE_ID=1189975702851 |title=Atle Eide joins HitecVision as partner |author=HitecVision Private Equity |date=2007-09-17 |accessdate=2008-11-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110711171819/http://www.hitecvision.com/htv/public/openIndex/view/page1.html?ARTICLE_ID=1189975702851 |archivedate=2011-07-11 |df= }}</ref>

Eide is a former board member of [[Fokus Bank]], [[Acta Holding|Acta]], [[Cermaq]] and [[SalMar]]. From 2003 to 2007 he was [[chief executive officer]] of [[Marine Harvest]].<ref name=hitec />

