{{Infobox person | name = Don Vebole | image = | alt = | caption = | birth_name = | birth_date = 1985 <!-- {{birth date and age|YYYY|MM|DD}} for living people. For people who have died, use {{Birth date|YYYY|MM|DD}}. --> | birth_place = | death_date = <!-- {{Death date and age|YYYY|MM|DD|YYYY|MM|DD}} (death date then birth date) --> | death_place = | nationality = French | other_names = | occupation = Entrepreneur, car designer | years_active = | known_for = Taurus World Angels | notable_works = | website={{URL|don-vebole.com}} }}
'''Don Vebole''' (born in February 1985) is a [[French people|French]] car stylist. Raised in the Parisian suburb of [[Seine-et-Marne|Seine et Marne]].<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=http://www.celebrityintelligence.com/news/Rl0/Matt-Damon-Lends-Support-To-Taurus-World-Angels|title=News - Matt Damon Lends Support To Taurus World Angels|website=www.celebrityintelligence.com|access-date=2016-05-31}}{{dead link|date=September 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=http://www.firstluxemag.com/la-personnalisation-des-voitures-de-luxe-par-don-vebole/|title=La personnalisation des voitures de luxe par Don Vebole {{!}} FIRSTLUXE|website=www.firstluxemag.com|access-date=2016-05-31}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite web|url=http://www.entreprises.ouest-france.fr/article/don-vebole-relooke-prix-dor-voitures-stars-19-09-2013-109938|title=Don Vebole relooke à prix d'or les voitures des stars|date=2012-04-27|website=Ouest France Entreprises|access-date=2016-05-31}}</ref><ref name=":3">{{Cite web|url=http://www.turbo.fr/actualite-automobile/536616-tuning-chronique-televisee-don-vebole/|title=Tuning : chronique télévisée pour Don Vebole|website=Turbo.fr|language=fr-fr|access-date=2016-05-31}}</ref>
==Early life and education== Following the break up of his parents, at 16, in order to help his family, he used his mechanical knowledge and painting and his inventive capacity to exercise his talent for customization and modification on mopeds and other two wheels mechanics of his relatives. <ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1" /><ref name=":2" /><ref name=":3" />
==Career== After obtaining his Bachelor in 2004, he moved to [[Tampa, Florida|Tampa Florida]] to perfect his customization techniques on luxury vehicles. After overcoming many challenges and obstacles and before his return to France in 2007, Don Vebole created Taurus USA. His creation was showcased at Tuning Show, the French car show in Paris in the city of [[Le Bourget]] .<ref name=":0" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.leblogauto.com/2013/07/un-cayenne-don-vebole-pour-une-etoile-montante-du-foot-francais.html|title=Un Cayenne Don Vebole pour une étoile montante du foot français {{!}} le blog auto|date=2013-07-25|website=le blog auto|access-date=2016-05-31}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.sportune.fr/article/djibril-cisse-pour-30-000e-offrez-vous-une-de-ses-voitures-2-74202|title=Djibril Cissé: Pour 30.000€, offrez-vous une de ses voitures|date=2012-09-13|website=Sportune|language=fr-FR|access-date=2016-05-31}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.footmercato.net/autre-championnat/insolites-les-perles-de-la-semaine_62866|title=Insolites : les perles de la semaine|website=Foot Mercato : Info Transferts Football - Actu Foot Transfert|access-date=2016-05-31}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.autodeclics.com/porsche/actualite_voiture/49693-remy_cabella_s_offre_un_porsche_cayenne_prepare.html|title=Un Porsche Cayenne " DON VEBOLE " pour Rémy Cabella|website=www.autodeclics.com|access-date=2016-05-31}}</ref>
In 2009, after participating only in two Parisian, French car shows, the director of the house Hamann Motorsport approached him to become the official distributor of the brand in France and [[Monaco]].<ref name=":0" />
After 3 years at [[Hamann Motorsport]], he decided to focus on developing and manufacturing his own brand with regards to parts and high-end automotive accessories.
